Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下七隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是全體出動了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,總攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的襲擊方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這一仗太有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,營養品都要增量了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,樹也要嗑藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這個說法有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊為什麼不馬上攻過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何 既然不能去神樹大人庇護不到的牆外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就沒辦法主動出擊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人似乎會從緊貼牆壁的位置發動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.61,Back,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,922.5)}咯吱咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不用緊張沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有大家在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好 勇者部眾人變身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人也是蠻拚的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,反過來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只要殲滅這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥等於結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 這裡來做那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那個？ 哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,圓…圓陣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,決戰需要氣勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了就請你們吃喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我要大吃特吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,肉片蓋澆烏龍麵什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你說我也會殲滅它們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我有想要實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,加油守護大家 守護國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喔！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================Title====================
