Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好 殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,宿命點的前進速度各有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那個巨大的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,壓迫力明顯不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,頭功歸我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是第一隻 封印掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 夏凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其他敵人到達前 先打倒這傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,轉什麼轉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,配合得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 剛才那敵人的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直是伸出臉來討打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是陷阱？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這個聲音怎麼回事 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這種程度 勇者的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是那個鈴鐺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,狙擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,聲音是讓大家幸福的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這種聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這種聲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是 你們倆！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好 三隻一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 解開繩索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,後退？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,潛下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,合體了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我可沒聽說過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但能一下打倒三隻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一併開始封印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這東西會跟蹤的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,既然會追過來 就原物奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,無效？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下樹 把大家捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人早早掛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這怎麼行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐… 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,解放積蓄的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者的殺手鐧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是…滿開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對敵軍實施總攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這種程度的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,看來都沒有封印的必要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,無論哪次都是這麼奇怪的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,離神樹大人好近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這隻宿命點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙 又小又快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,被輕易躲過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,休想破壞我們的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不許去那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,懲罰你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小樹 太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 我要躺到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,樹 做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼 這個看起來很難纏的有精神的球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部全員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,封印開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我纏住這傢伙 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也給我留下點甜頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好 不愧是勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,風前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒那傢伙！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,無論哪方面 都太破天荒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而且那個御靈 出現的地方是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那種東西 要怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,最後的最後 居然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因為是御靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只要像先前那樣對付就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,無論敵人多麼巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能放棄呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂勇者 就是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,應該能帶上友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 封印就拜託你們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快點殲滅掉它喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 侵蝕好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拘束力要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,御靈會攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓它落到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 友奈 看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一個也不會讓它通過的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,來到這裡了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,看著吧 我去幹掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,滿開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,守護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成為勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,勇…勇者部五條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其一！ 盡量不放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再來！ 五條！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又一條！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,車到山前！ 多半！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有路！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,風頭都被我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,搶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我用最後的力量 保住了這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知能不能撐得住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人會保佑我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就算萬一失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有友奈在一起 我不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓兩人平安歸來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對會救下她們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持得不錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 樹 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是你止住的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,去接她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 我…努力了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,營養品… 早知道就嗑點了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 東鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你們振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是… 姑且還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 你們真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,早點回話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 因為紅顏才薄命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我這種總能化險為夷…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢 好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是三好夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,與宿命點交戰 負傷者4名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,希望馬上安排靈力醫療班
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 通過本次戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,12隻宿命點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,全部被殲滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,被我們贊州中學勇者部！
